headline: Shopify-Friendly Payment Solution for Cannabis Seeds Touted by Established Provider
summary: Organic Payment Gateways has placed an emphasis on a new payment gateway and merchant account service for Q4 2025, tailored for Shopify merchants who sell legal cannabis seeds online. This specialized solution allows these online seed retailers to accept credit card payments on their Shopify websites, even if mainstream providers such as their bank, Shopify Payments, Square, Stripe, or PayPal have previously turned them away under more restrictive policies.
